This request is SERVER ONLY. Creates an authenticated user session from an Auth Token obtained from WGNI.  Request URL  POST   https://api-wgie.wargaming.net/auth/api/v1/loginWithAuthToken  Request Sample  {
   header : {
     message_id :  9fb0c554-132d-441c-b32c-1e13929852c0 
  },
   body : {
     region :  na ,
     auth_token :  JC0yZReLvfQPi76y2F5A4Q ,
     wgid : 18414499,
     fingerprint :  a5d1cf90-f38c-4775-80cd-84e3fb76b509 ,
     create_remember_me : true,
     client_ip :  178.172.239.244 ,
     auth_token_target_application :  xmppcs 
  }
}  Curl  curl -X POST --header 'Content-Type: application/json' --header 
'Accept: application/json' --header 
'x-freya-server-api-key: test' -d '{
   header : {
     message_id :  9fb0c554-132d-441c-b32c-1e13929852c0 
  },
   body : {
     region :  na ,
     auth_token :  JC0yZReLvfQPi76y2F5A4Q ,
     wgid : 18414499,
     fingerprint :  a5d1cf90-f38c-4775-80cd-84e3fb76b509 ,
     create_remember_me : true,
     client_ip :  178.172.239.244 ,
     auth_token_target_application :  xmppcs 
  }
}' 'https://api-wgie.wargaming.net/auth/api/v1/loginWithAuthToken'   Parameters     Name  Description  Type      x-freya-server-api-key  Authentication API key.  string    message_id  For tracking or debugging purposes. Returns back in the response.  string, optional    region  SPA region.  string, optional    auth_token  Wargaming Auth Token.  string    wgid  Wargaming Account ID.  int    fingerprint  A unique device fingerprint that stays consistent for a given user and device.  string, optional    create_remember_me  Boolean indicating if a Remember Me Token should be created.  boolean, optional    client_ip  Client IP address.  boolean, optional    auth_token_target_application  If not null, will create Auth Token for specified application.  string, optional     Response Sample  {
   header : {
     message_id :  9fb0c554-132d-441c-b32c-1e13929852c0 
  },
   body : {
     success : true,
     result_message : null,
     result_code : null,
     profile_id : 93503539,
     nickname :  Player1990 ,
     client_session :  salAzJiufFWCCT3rXiA79A ,
     client_gateway : null,
     remember_me :  2:4758258918403912621:77218061794558285652020638946378270086 ,
     auth_token :  65079312 ,
     wgid : 18414499
     first_login : false,
     restrictions : [],
     pending_order_id :  0 
  } }  While most of the response values are self-explanatory, some may need clarification.   client_session  — Client session token.  first_login  — Indicates whether this login instance is the first ever for this player.  restrictions  — If not empty, provides the details of player's restrictions (for example, bans).  pending_order_id  — Initial Inventory Order ID. 0 if order is complete or there is no initial inventory. If non-zero — use  getPurchaseStatusByOrderId .

