Recursively get profile's and its children's entitlements and virtual currency balances.  Request URL  POST   https://api-wgie.wargaming.net/server/api/v1/getFullInventory  Request Sample  {
   header : {
     message_id :  9fb0c554-132d-441c-b32c-1e13929852c0 
  },
   body : {
     profile_id : 93503539
  }
}  Curl  curl -X POST --header 'Content-Type: application/json' --header 'Accept: application/json' --header 
'x-freya-server-api-key: test' -d '{
   header : {
   message_id :  9fb0c554-132d-441c-b32c-1e13929852c0 
  },
   body : {
     profile_id : 93503539
  }
}' 'https://api-wgie.wargaming.net/server/api/v1/getFullInventory'   Parameters     Name  Description  Type      x-freya-server-api-key  Authentication API key.  string    message_id  For tracking or debugging purposes. Returns back in the response.  string, optional    profile_id  Profile ID returned during the authentication flow.  int     Response Sample  {
   header : {
     message_id :  9fb0c554-132d-441c-b32c-1e13929852c0 
  },
   body : {
     success : true,
     result_message :  string ,
     result_code :  string ,
     profile : {
       entitlements : [
        {
           entitlement_code :  regular_repair_kit ,
           amount : 2,
           expiration : 0
        }
      ],
       currencies : [
        {
           currency_id :  gold ,
           currency_code :  1 ,
           amount :  1000 
        }
      ],
       profile_id : 93503539,
       game_data :  Game supplied string when child profile was created. ,
       children : [ {} ]
    }
  }
}

